name: Reverb

inputs.name: Room size
inputs.description: The sense of space to the audio [0,1.5]

inputs.name: Stereo Balance
inputs.description: Adjust the left and right channel ratio of the output, the louder the sound, the more to the left channel [0, 1.0]

inputs.name: Wet
inputs.description: The mix rate of the reverb effect to the final audio [0, 1.0]

inputs.name: Dry
inputs.description: The mix rate of the original audio to the final audio [0, 1.0]

inputs.name: Wet Gain
inputs.description: The volume of mix rate of the reverb effect to the final audio [0, 1.0]

inputs.name: Dry Gain
inputs.description: The volume mix rate of the original audio to the final audio[0, 1.0]

outputs.name: Audio
outputs.description: Execute this node,  connect to a speaker to play the audio stream

description: Create a sense of space or depth to the audio
